<sect1 id="accessx-applet-introduction">
<title>用法</title>
<!-- ==== Figure ============================================= -->
	 <figure id="accessx-applet-fig"> 
		<title>键盘辅助功能监视器</title> 
		<screenshot> 
		  <mediaobject> 
			 <imageobject><imagedata fileref="figures/accessx-status-applet.png" format="PNG"/> 
			 </imageobject>
			 <textobject> 
				<phrase>显示键盘辅助功能监视器，包含一排图标，显示了键盘当前状态。</phrase> 
			 </textobject> 
		  </mediaobject> 
		</screenshot> 
	 </figure> 
    <!-- ==== End of Figure ======================================= -->
<para><application>键盘辅助功能监视器</application> 给您显示键盘辅助功能特性的状态，当它们启用的时候。例如，您可以看到当前哪一个修饰键被激活，哪一个键盘模拟鼠标键被按下。</para>
<para>更多如何使用键盘辅助功能特性，请参阅： <ulink url="ghelp:gnome-access-guide">桌面辅助功能指南</ulink>。</para>

<sect2 id="accessx-status-interpreting">
<title>小程序所显示的内容</title>
<para>
  <informaltable>
    <tgroup cols="2">
      <colspec colname="col1" colwidth="0.81"/><colspec colname="col2" colwidth="1.19*"/>
      <thead>
	<row valign="top">
	  <entry colname="col1">
	    <para>图标</para>
	  </entry>
	  <entry colname="col">
	    <para>含义</para>
	  </entry>
	</row>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
	<row valign="top">
	  <entry colname="col1">
	    <para>
	      <inlinemediaobject><imageobject>
		<imagedata fileref="figures/accessx-status-disabled.png" format="PNG"/>
	      </imageobject><textobject><phrase>回弹键</phrase>
	    </textobject></inlinemediaobject>
	    </para>
	  </entry>
	  <entry colname="col2">
	    <para>辅助特性当前被禁用。</para>
	  </entry>
	</row>
	<row valign="top">
	  <entry colname="col1">
	    <para>
	      <inlinemediaobject><imageobject>
		<imagedata fileref="figures/accessx_bounce-keys.png" format="PNG"/>
	      </imageobject><textobject><phrase>回弹键</phrase>
	    </textobject></inlinemediaobject>
	    </para>
	  </entry>
	  <entry colname="col2">
	    <para>启用了回弹键。</para>
	  </entry>
	</row>
	<row valign="top">
	  <entry colname="col1">
	    <para>
	      <inlinemediaobject><imageobject>
		<imagedata fileref="figures/accessx_mouse-keys.png" format="PNG"/>
	      </imageobject><textobject><phrase>鼠标键</phrase>
	    </textobject></inlinemediaobject>
	    </para>
	  </entry>
	  <entry colname="col2">
	    <para>启用了模拟鼠标键。</para>
	  </entry>
	</row>
	<row valign="top">
	  <entry colname="col1">
	    <para>
	      <inlinemediaobject><imageobject>
		<imagedata fileref="figures/accessx_slow-keys.png" format="PNG"/>
	      </imageobject><textobject><phrase>回弹键</phrase>
	    </textobject></inlinemediaobject>
	    </para>
	  </entry>
	  <entry colname="col2">
	    <para>启用了慢速键。</para>
	  </entry>
	</row>
	<row valign="top">
	  <entry colname="col1">
	    <para>
	      <inlinemediaobject><imageobject>
		<imagedata fileref="figures/accessx_sticky-keys.png" format="PNG"/>
	      </imageobject><textobject><phrase>粘滞键</phrase>
	    </textobject></inlinemediaobject>
	    </para>
	  </entry>
	  <entry colname="col2">
	    <para>启用了粘滞键。这儿表示 <keycap>Shift</keycap> 键按了一次，<keycap>Ctrl</keycap> 键按了两次。</para>
	  </entry>
	</row>
	<row valign="top">
	  <entry colname="col1">
	    <para>
	      <inlinemediaobject><imageobject>
		<imagedata fileref="figures/accessx_sticky-altGr-key.png" format="PNG"/>
	      </imageobject><textobject><phrase><keycap>AltGr 键</keycap> 键的图标</phrase>
	    </textobject></inlinemediaobject>
	    </para>
	  </entry>
	  <entry colname="col2">
	    <para><keycap>AltGr</keycap> 键按了一次。</para>
	  </entry>
	</row>
	<row valign="top">
	  <entry colname="col1">
	    <para>
	      <inlinemediaobject><imageobject>
		<imagedata fileref="figures/accessx_sticky-meta-key.png" format="PNG"/>
	      </imageobject><textobject><phrase><keycap>Meta 键</keycap> 键的图标</phrase>
	    </textobject></inlinemediaobject>
	    </para>
	  </entry>
	  <entry colname="col2">
	    <para><keycap>Meta</keycap> 键按了一次。</para>
	  </entry>
	</row>
	<row valign="top">
	  <entry colname="col1">
	    <para>
	      <inlinemediaobject><imageobject>
		<imagedata fileref="figures/accessx_sticky-windows-key.png" format="PNG"/>
	      </imageobject><textobject><phrase><keycap>Windows 键</keycap> 标志的按键</phrase>
	    </textobject></inlinemediaobject>
	    </para>
	  </entry>
	  <entry colname="col2">
	    <para><keycap>Windows</keycap> 徽标键按了一次。</para>
	  </entry>
	</row>
	<row valign="top">
	  <entry colname="col1">
	    <para>
	      <inlinemediaobject><imageobject>
		<imagedata fileref="figures/accessx_sticky-shift-key.png" format="PNG"/>
	      </imageobject><textobject><phrase>Shift 图标</phrase>
	    </textobject></inlinemediaobject>
	    </para>
	  </entry>
	  <entry colname="col2">
	    <para><keycap>Shift</keycap> 键按了一次。</para>
	  </entry>
	</row>
      </tbody>
    </tgroup>
  </informaltable>
 </para>
</sect2>
